{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"unref"},{"kind":"text","text":"()"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Once the reference count reaches zero, the directory will be closed and all","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"resources associated with it will be freed. If [method","type":"text"},{"code":"GLib.Dir.close","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called when the reference count is greater than zero, the directory is closed","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"but the ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDir"},{"text":" structure will not be freed until its reference count reaches","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"zero."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"It is an error to call any of the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDir"},{"text":" methods other than","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"[method","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Dir.ref"},{"type":"text","text":"] and [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GLib.Dir.unref"},{"type":"text","text":"] on a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDir"},{"text":" after calling","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"GLib.Dir.close","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] on it.","type":"text"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/glib\/dirprotocol\/unref()"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib","doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DirProtocol"]]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GLib\/documentation\/GLib\/DirProtocol\/unref()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract"